    public class ImporterWorker

    • Constructor Detail

      • ImporterWorker

        public ImporterWorker(DBConfig dbConfig,
              int datasetIdent,
              Dataset sourceDataset)
        Constructs a new instance of ImporterWorker that will export triples from a sourceDataset and import them in the indicated DB. Triples will be loaded in the tables of the database that are indicated by the parameter datasetIdent.
        Parameters:
        dbConfig - database configuration
        datasetIdent - PostGISImporter.DATASET_A for dataset A or PostGISImporter.DATASET_B for dataset B
        sourceDataset - source dataset from which to extract triples
        Throws:
        RuntimeException - in case of an unrecoverable error. The cause of the error will be encapsulated by the thrown RuntimeException
